\text{2) Linear Transformations:}
\bar{X} = \frac{1}{n}\mathbf{1}^T X \quad \text{where } \mathbf{1} = (1,\ldots,1)^T
S^2 = \frac{1}{n-1}(I - \frac{1}{n}\mathbf{1}\mathbf{1}^T)X \cdot X

